skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: spacecoast freewheelers
des: This skill lets you ask for the rides and events from the Spacecoast Freewheelers Cycling Club based in Brevard county, Florida. You no longer have to open the browser and go to the SCFW website to get the latest rides and events. Ask Alexa and get ready to ride!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
